{"tid":2319853,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇fg一樣返工返到好大壓力","createTime":"2020-12-10T11:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:02:01.000Z","uid":57476,"like":13,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"68a0a593ff9ddcad943671eea7b36aafaf581429","tid":2319853,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"符碌因為某啲原因入咗間香港幾大嘅公司讀<br />\n本生係社科撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以就算個位唔係自己想做嘅都頂硬上，冇人際關係CV空白一片仲要社科知自己一定揸兜<br />\n返咗就快半年，份工其實好得意，同事都一家人咁，成team最細大家都幾錫自己<br />\n<br />\n問題係我日日覺得自己係舊垃圾拖條team後腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗係咪唔應該留係度阻住人，但心知一quit自己咁屎一定冇工請 (grad前後搵intern/工都冇回音)<br />\n<br />\n成日偷偷地返工喊，覺得好大壓力呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 屋企窮，唔返工要日日睇老母臉色仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0474a5a800534fe7271d3b0aa4294559e1cce8e","tid":2319853,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"騎牛搵馬囉"},{"pid":"8f8d34d878de1dd355ab2aa9af081aa41354e32b","tid":2319853,"uid":154373,"like":18,"dislike":13,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"做女人已經係easy mode 唔該知足"},{"pid":"ecc1a7f80851e80ddff93d03b2fd613c3ee07f9c","tid":2319853,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"1299?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d623f2aec0cb8104317e4a2a73a00c05fcb3e35f","tid":2319853,"uid":353267,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8f8d34d878de1dd355ab2aa9af081aa41354e32b","tid":2319853,"uid":154373,"like":18,"dislike":13,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"做女人已經係easy mode 唔該知足"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">真 <br />\n我肯定你唔係後生女實入唔到去做<br />\n而in你